# Screen Pet - Senior Cursor Rules

## Muc tieu du an
- Android only, Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, Material 3.
- Ung dung **pet / animation tren man hinh** (Screen Pet): hien thi va tuong tac voi nhan vat pet trong app; mo rong overlay he thong chi khi da thiet ke ro va tach tang.
- Kien truc bat buoc: MVVM + Clean Architecture + feature-based.
- San sang release Google Play (AAB).

## Cau truc bat buoc
- `app/core`: constants (bao gom duong dan asset pet/animation), utils, theme, navigation, di.
- `app/feature/...`: tach `presentation`, `domain`, `data` theo tung feature (vi du `pet`, `home`, `settings` — dat ten theo roadmap, khong tron layer).
- Khong duoc tron layer.

## Luong nghiep vu bat buoc
- `UI -> ViewModel -> UseCase -> Repository -> DataSource`

## Cam tuyet doi
- Khong viet business logic trong Composable.
- Khong goi API/database truc tiep tu UI.
- Khong de ViewModel phu thuoc `Context`.
- Khong bo qua ranh gioi MVVM/Clean Architecture.
- Khong tu code khi chua ro yeu cau (mo ho).
- Cai gi chua biet co the search hoi lai user.

## Quy tac Compose
- Dung Compose only, khong XML screen.
- State hoist, UI uu tien stateless.
- State den tu ViewModel (StateFlow uu tien).
- Toan bo ui state phai immutable.

## Quy tac Animation / Pet UI
- Duong dan asset (Lottie, WebP, anh sprite, sound) phai qua constant trong `app/core/constants`, khong hardcode chuoi path trong Composable.
- Giam tai main thread: decode/giai nen nang o tang data hoac background phu hop; tranh logic nang trong `LaunchedEffect`/composition vo han.
- Trang thai animation (idle, tap, feed, ...) do ViewModel/UseCase dieu phoi; UI chi nhan state va trigger event.
- Neu dung **overlay / cua so he thong**: tach `Service` hoac tang rieng, khong tron truc tiep vao man hinh Composable thuan; xu ly quyen va lifecycle ro rang.

## Quy tac DI + Data
- DI dung Hilt, khong tao singleton thu cong.
- Repository la single source of truth.
- **DataStore** uu tien cho: cai dat nhe, trang thai pet (ten, skin da mo), flag onboarding.
- **Room / SQLite** chi khi can lich su / truy van phuc tap (vi du nhat ky cham soc, thong ke theo ngay); khong bat buoc moi thu deu vao SQLite.

## Quy tac luu tru (khi co)
- Moi thao tac doc/ghi DB phai di qua `Repository -> DataSource`.
- Can co migration khi thay doi schema Room, tranh mat du lieu nguoi dung.

## Quy tac code
- Code phai sach, de doc, de test, va tuan thu day du nguyen ly SOLID.
- Ten bien/ham ro nghia, SRP, tranh duplicate.
- Comment chi khi logic phuc tap.
- Comment code bat buoc bang tieng Viet.
- Moi file khong duoc vuot qua 100 dong (uu tien tach nho theo trach nhiem).
- Moi function nen nho gon, mot trach nhiem ro rang.

## Quy tac MVVM + DI bat buoc
- Bat buoc ap dung dung mo hinh MVVM cho toan bo feature.
- UI layer chi render state va gui event, khong chua business logic.
- ViewModel chi lam viec voi UseCase/Repository, khong truy cap datasource truc tiep.
- Dependency Injection bat buoc dung Hilt, khong khoi tao thu cong trong code nghiep vu.

## Quy tac ngon ngu
- Assistant tra loi bang tieng Viet.
- Giai thich tai lieu tieng Anh bang tieng Viet.

## Quy tac UI / theme
- Mau / chu / kich thuoc dua vao token `app/core/theme`.
- Khong hardcode string / mau / dimens trong screen (dung string resource hoac token).

## Quy tac release
- Build debug/release phai xanh truoc khi chot.
- Khong de debug log rac trong ban release.
- Uu tien thay doi nho, an toan, de test.

## Error Handling
- Tat ca data tra ve phai wrap trong Result (Success/Error) o tang domain/data phu hop.
- UI phai co state: Loading / Success / Error khi can.
- Khong throw exception truc tiep len UI.
- Loi phai duoc xu ly tai ViewModel.

## UI State
- Moi screen chi co 1 UiState duy nhat.
- State phai immutable.
- Khong dung nhieu StateFlow le cho cung mot man.

## Testing
- UseCase bat buoc co unit test.
- ViewModel phai test StateFlow.
- Repository co the dung fake data de test.

## Monetization
- Logic quang cao phai tach rieng (khong viet truc tiep trong UI).
- Khong lam gian doan trai nghiem nguoi dung.
- Ads chi hien thi o thoi diem hop ly (sau action, khong spam).

## Navigation
- Navigation chi duoc goi tu UI layer.
- Khong navigate trong ViewModel.
- Route duoc dinh nghia trong `core/navigation`.
- Uu tien don gian, ship nhanh, khong over-engineering.

## Skill Android
- `.cursor/skill_androi`: dung skill Android de hoc va viet code, tham khao tranh loi vat.
- Kotlin / Compose viet theo muc senior (5–10 nam kinh nghiem): ro rang, bao tri tot.
